data.description: Great family home in established Woodstock neighborhood. Playground, pool, tennis, basketball court, fitness center all within walking distance to grocery store, eateries and shopping. Location is key only being minutes to I575 with no interstate noise as well as minutes to downtown Woodstock with all of its quaint small-town charm. This is a newer home in immaculate condition. BEST VALUE!
